Baiklah, ayolah.

00:15:29.280 --> 00:15:30.240
Pegang ini.

00:15:30.880 --> 00:15:32.040
Sangat bagus.

00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:52.440
Vinayak belum keluar.

00:15:52.440 --> 00:15:54.920
Anda harus bertanya
kepada guru kelasnya.

00:15:55.280 --> 00:15:56.200
Oke terima kasih.

00:16:45.720 --> 00:16:46.680
Rumah..

